message.content: The likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper are "cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE". This is because the paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for question answering, which are relevant to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and neural networks (cs.NE).
